Output assets/release-fix-scan.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontFamily "Menlo"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 30
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "npx aislop fix ../daily"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 18s

Type "npx aislop scan ../daily"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 12s

Sleep 2s
